quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,38,"Nikhuboola mbu, “Yishe okhurulamwo mwesi. Ne toto obulunjifu okhurula khwisie bulabetsela. Kho, abaloonda obulunjifu bwanje obo, shibaliba noburi, ne shibalibeelela tawe."
  2,39,"Ne balia abakhaya mana nibakatsula ebimanyisio biefu, abo nibo abaliba abandu bomumulilo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi.""
  2,40,"Enywe Abana ba Israili! Yitsulile tsimbabaasi tsianje tsiandabahelesia, ne khole shinga khwalakana, nasi ndilikhola shinga khwalakana, ne murie Esie butswa."
  2,41,"Ne suubile kalia akandeshia akonga omukhono akamulinako, ne mulaba abambeli okhukakhaya tawe, ne mulakusia ebimanyisio bianje khubukusi obutiti tawe, ne murie Esie butswa."
  2,42,"Ne mulasaasia obwatoto nende obubeyi tawe, ne mulafisa obwatoto nanyu nimumanyile tawe."
  2,43,"Ne swaliye khatsotso, ne rusie eshihanwa shia izakaa, ne iname halala nende benamanga."
  2,44,"Koo, mloomesinjia abandu okhukhola amalayi, nanyu abeene mwiyibilila, nanyu musomanga Eshitabu, shimurumushilanga obwongo tawe?"
  2,45,"Ne khaabe obukhoonyi khulwokhwifwila nende khulwokhulaama, ne toto ako namakhongo muno halali khubalia abehotselefu."
  2,46,"Balia abasuubilanga mbu toto baliakana nende Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, ne mbu toto balikalukha ewuwe."
  2,47,"Enywe Abana ba Israili! Yitsulile tsimbabaasi tsianje etsia ndabahelesia, ne toto Esie ndabakholela obulai muno okhushilakho ebiloonje bindi bioosi."
  2,48,"Ne rie inyanga ya omundu alalikhoonya owundi liosiliosi tawe, ne shalisabila yesiyesi eshileshelo tawe, ne shiosishiosi shiokhununula sishilibukulwa okhurula khuye tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe."